esse lugar limpo?

151
00:09:03,172 --> 00:09:05,271
Spam.
Spam.

152
00:09:05,332 --> 00:09:08,138
Stewie Meyers,
Sr. Campbell, Sr. Raimi.

153
00:09:08,206 --> 00:09:12,483
